@startuml sequence_build_docx
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Sequence — Build DOCX Resume

actor "Quinntyne Brown" as User
participant "build-resume.ps1" as Script
participant "Pandoc" as Pandoc
participant "resumes/" as Output

User -> Script : Invoke with -InputFile <path>
Script -> Script : Determine output directory\n(base/ or tailored/)
Script -> Pandoc : pandoc <input> --to docx\n--reference-doc=templates/reference.docx\n-o <output>.docx
Pandoc --> Script : DOCX file written to output path
Script -> Output : Move/confirm DOCX in correct subdirectory
Output --> User : <basename>.docx ready

@enduml
